articles.title: Everything that happened on MotoGP testing day one - The Race
articles.description: Jorge Martin and Pedro Acosta led the way on the opening day of collective MotoGP testing at Sepang, with Marc Marquez ninth.
articles.content:
MotoGP title hopeful Jorge Martin led rookie sensation Pedro Acosta on the opening day of the three-day pre-season test at Sepang.
